These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apple, tomato, watermelon
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, august, june
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, water-polo, weightlifting
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, orange, turquise
 1. the person who likes turquise is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person eating apple##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person eating tomato is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite        | lemonade |
| Food          | watermelon    | tomato        | apple    |
| Birthday   | june        | march        | august    |
| Pet           | turtle        | chinchilla    | rabbit   |
| Sport         | water-polo    | weightlifting | climbing |
| Color     | orange     | apricot          | turquise     |

