.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, poker
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, paramedic, software-developer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, zombie
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, polish, turkish
City: nizza, miami, new-york
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, train
1. the electrician is the turkish##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the turkish is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
8. the electrician is on the right of the person playing poker##1
9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Game         | poker    | mah-jongg     | whist            |
| Job           | paramedic | electrician | software-developer |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | satire      | zombie             |
| Nationality   | malaysian | turkish     | polish             |
| City         | miami  | new-york       | nizza           |
| Transport     | train     | motorbike   | jet-ski            |

