2. the american is on the far left##1
3. the person playing whist is the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person playing poker is on the right of the german##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person playing go is the person eating peach##1
7. the person playing poker is the person watching western movies##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person eating corn##1
9. the canadian is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | video-games  | cooking     | skydiving    |
| Job           | photographer | dressmaker  | videographer |
