 2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the firefighter is on the right of the american##1
 4. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
 5. the british is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the manager is the person playing snooker##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the architect##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the firefighter##1
10. the british is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |
| Food          | broccoli | nectarine | plum        |
| City         | san-francisco  | nizza   | edinburgh     |
| Job           | manager  | architect | firefighter |
| Game   | snooker  | bridge   | monopoly     |
| Nationality   | british  | american  | german      |
| Pet           | rabbit   | rat       | goat        |

