.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, corn, mango
3 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, whist
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, old-henry, fonseca
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, russian
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, weightlifting
1. the old-henry-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating corn##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the chinese is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person playing backgammon##1
6. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
7. the person playing whist is the owner of the cat##1
8. the chinese is on the far left##1
9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Food          | corn          | mango      | apricot      |
| Game         | whist        | bridge | backgammon      |
| Cigar   | game          | old-henry        | fonseca       |
| Nationality   | chinese       | nigerian   | russian      |
| Pet           | cat           | mouse      | bird         |
| Sport         | weightlifting | cycling    | snowboarding |

 